  "写入单元格与设置区域": "Write cells and set a range",
  "写入": "Write",
  "用赋值给 .Value 往 B2 写入一个数，再用 Range(\"A1:C1\").Value 给一整行三个单元格同时赋同一个值。": "Assign to .Value to write a number into B2, then use Range(\"A1:C1\").Value to fill three cells in a row with the same value at once.",
  "写入和读取是同一个属性 .Value，只是放在等号的哪一边不同：读在右边，写在左边。": "Writing and reading use the same .Value property; only the side of the equals sign differs: read on the right, write on the left.",
  "Range(\"A1:C1\") 用冒号表示一个连续区域，给它的 .Value 赋一个标量，整片都会变成那个值。": "Range(\"A1:C1\") uses a colon for a contiguous block; assigning a scalar to its .Value fills the whole block with that value.",
  "别用循环挨个写 A1、B1、C1——一次给整个区域赋值更快也更清楚。": "Don't loop over A1, B1, C1 one by one — assigning the whole range at once is faster and clearer.",
  "给 B2 的 .Value 赋值 100": "Assign 100 to B2's .Value",
  "用 ws.Range(\"B2\").Value = 100 写入。": "Use ws.Range(\"B2\").Value = 100 to write.",
  "给区域 A1:C1 一次性赋值": "Fill the range A1:C1 at once",
